info.title: Inbound Delivery (A2X)
info.description: This service enables you to create, read, update and delete inbound deliveries. It can be consumed in Fiori apps and on other user interfaces.

x-sap-shortText: Process inbound deliveries using this synchronous inbound service

values.text: [Delivery Processing Without Order Reference(1MI)](https://me.sap.com/processnavigator/SolP/1MI " Link To BP ")
[Direct Procurement with Inbound Delivery(2TX)](https://me.sap.com/processnavigator/SolP/2TX " Link To BP ")

x-sap-extensible.description:
API can be extended by custom fields on the following business contexts (field usage for this API needs to be selected):
* Shipping: Delivery (LE_SHP_DELIVERY)
* Shipping: Delivery Item (LE_SHP_DELIVERYITEM)

[How to add an extension field to an API](https://help.sap.com/docs/SAP_S4HANA_CLOUD/0f69f8fb28ac4bf48d2b57b9637e81fa/ce819b8557194ae0aa180ba4ac6a04de.html)

get.description: Reads all inbound delivery items. You can narrow down the result by specifying filter conditions.

parameters.name: $filter
parameters.description: Filter items by property values, see [Filtering](https://help.sap.com/doc/5890d27be418427993fafa6722cdc03b/Cloud/en-US/OdataV2.pdf#page=64)

post.summary: Creates an additional batch split item for an inbound delivery item.
post.description: Creates an additional batch split item for the specified inbound delivery item and optionally sets the delivery quantity and batch-related fields.

parameters.name: BatchBySupplier
parameters.description: Value needs to be enclosed in single quotes

parameters.name: ManufactureDate
parameters.description:
Time Stamp  
(Value needs to be enclosed in single quotes and prefixed with `datetime`, e.g. `datetime'2017-12-31T00:00'`)

parameters.name: ShelfLifeExpirationDate
parameters.description:
Time Stamp  
(Value needs to be enclosed in single quotes and prefixed with `datetime`, e.g. `datetime'2017-12-31T00:00'`)

parameters.name: ActualDeliveryQuantity
parameters.description: Value needs to be suffixed with `M`

parameters.name: Batch
parameters.description: Value needs to be enclosed in single quotes

parameters.name: DeliveryDocument
parameters.description: Value needs to be enclosed in single quotes

parameters.name: DeliveryDocumentItem
parameters.description: Value needs to be enclosed in single quotes

parameters.name: DeliveryQuantityUnit
parameters.description: Value needs to be enclosed in single quotes

parameters.name: PutawayQuantityInOrderUnit
parameters.description: Value needs to be suffixed with `M`
